    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Tachydromia maculipennis Walker, male (Canada, Ontario; CNC). A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Hypopygium, dorsal view. C. Right epandrial lamella and right surstylus, lateral view. D. Left epandrial lamella and left surstylus, lateral view. Abbreviations: cerc—cercus; epand—epandrium; hypd—hypandrium; lft sur—left surstylus; rt sur—right surstylus. B–D: scale bar is 0.1 mm." ;
